    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We suggest a minimal model to describe the evolution of daily deaths due to Covid-19 in the European Union (EU) and UK, without any epidemiological hypothesis. Assuming current lockdown conditions were to remain in place, as of May 3rd 2020, this\n                  <jats:italic>ad hoc</jats:italic>\n                  fitting model is forecasting a total of 204 586 deaths in the EU. We could currently be at 2/3 of the total casualty count, and reach an overall death rate of one over 2 500 people.\n                </jats:p>",
